Company Overview of Macrocure Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Macrocure Ltd., a biotechnology company, focuses on developing, manufacturing, and commercializing novel cell therapy products for the treatment of chronic and other hard-to-heal wounds in Israel. Macrocure Ltd. was founded in 2008 and is headquartered in Petach Tikva, Israel. As of January 23, 2017, Macrocure Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Leap Therapeutics, Inc.


