Macrocure (NASDAQ:MCUR) & Mallinckrodt PLC (MNK) Head-To-Head Survey

					Posted by David on Jul 20th, 2017 // No Comments 



Macrocure (NASDAQ: MCUR) and Mallinckrodt PLC (NYSE:MNK) are both healthcare companies, but which is the better investment? We will contrast the two companies based on the strength of their valuation, analyst recommendations, institutional ownership, risk, dividends, earnings and profitabiliy. 
Profitability


